title: Humble Crew Toy Organizer with Shelf and 9 Storage Bins, Espresso/White
features: Removable toy storage bins for playtime and easy clean up.
Sturdy engineered wood construction frame reinforced with steel dowels, 20 pound weight capacity per level.
9 durable and interchangeable plastic storage bins, 6 standard and 3 large sized. BPA and phthalate free.
Neutral dark wooden finish with white colored toy bins and top storage shelf
Product Dimensions– Organizer: 34"W x 11"D (16"D with stabilizing braces) x 32"H, Standard bin sizing: 12"L x 9"W x 6"H, Large bin sizing: 16"L x 12"W x 6"H
Assembly required. Includes all hardware. Stabilizing braces provided for additional safety support.
description: Playtime is more fun when your kids can easily take out their toys, books and games and then quickly clean up afterwards. The space-saving Humble Crew Toy Storage Organizer with Shelf and 9 Storage Bins stows your children's toys in easy-to-see, easy-to-access BPA and phthalate free plastic storage bins. 6 standard and 3 large storage containers are easy to remove, replace and reposition along the 3 tiered shelves—sized just right within the toy organizer for toddlers and preschool-aged children. The top ledge on this kid's storage unit is the perfect space to display books, dolls or other favorite small toys, pictures and other decorative items, providing an additional level of easy-to-see and easy-to-access open storage for your convenience. It makes a great toy box storage alternative, helping keep your little one’s room clean and organized while at the same time teaching sorting and cognitive skills. The stylish colorway makes this the perfect organizational solution for bedrooms, nurseries, playrooms and classrooms. Made with a sturdy engineered wood construction frame and steel shelving rods, each level can hold up to 20 pounds. Some assembly is required and all hardware is included. Product sizing – 34"W x 11"D (16"D with stabilizing braces) x 32"H Standard bin sizing: 12"L x 9"W x 6"H Large bin sizing: 16"L x 12"W x 6"H Additional plastic storage toy bins are also sold separately
